properties.areaDesc: Oahu Windward Waters; Maui County Leeward Waters
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued February 14 at 9:19AM HST until February 17 at 6:00AM HST by NWS Honolulu HI
properties.description:
* WHAT...East winds 15 to 25 kt with higher gusts and seas 7 to
12 feet.

* WHERE...Oahu Windward Waters and Maui County Leeward Waters.

* WHEN...Until 6 AM HST Monday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
A Small Craft Advisory means that wind speeds of 25 to 33 knots
and/or seas 10 feet or greater are expected to produce conditions
hazardous to small craft. Inexperienced mariners, especially
those operating smaller vessels, should avoid navigating in these
conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 6 AM HST MONDAY
